      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1995 BMW M3 (E36) featuring the iconic S50B30 inline-six power plant with a meticulously maintained VANOS system for optimal torque delivery. This specimen boasts a seamless ZF 5-speed manual gearbox paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power distribution. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a suspension overhauled with Bilstein B8 dampers and period-correct bushings to maintain its legendary lateral grip. The exterior retains its factory-applied Alpine White finish with zero evidence of clear coat failure or panel misalignment. Inside, the 'Vader' sport seats show no bolster wear, and the dashboard remains free of UV-induced warping. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive cooling system refresh\u2014including a metal-impeller water pump and aluminum radiator\u2014to ensure thermal stability under spirited driving. A truly turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
